{"tid":143690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇左初戀日記：賤男蜜擾","createTime":"2017-03-04T19:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T19:25:35.000Z","uid":78686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf183f35ac50307f7fd2751fd4e4b21b33ecbda0","tid":143690,"uid":78686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:19:09.000Z","msg":"話說同朋友食完飯無野做 諗住睇下即場電影<br />\n好耐無睇港產片 <br />\n岩岩同睇完套戲<br />\n唔可以稱得上大制製作 但輕輕鬆鬆兩個鐘 絕對好過好多偽港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事貼地 經歷既事應該都勾起唔少90頭巴絲既回憶<br />\n同埋好耐都無一個香港女Artist令到我有心跳加速既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nVenus佢完全做到果種學生時代好Pure好Ture 出黎做野時好成熟既Feel<br />\n但當然演技可以再進步D<br />\n就係因為套戲夠寫實 所以可以令到一個失戀既人無限FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎咁多位討論下 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">利申：非打手 只係覺得唔好因爲無大卡士而唔睇呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"6149b6b406d55136cd9cf4afaa55807d676defbc","tid":143690,"uid":78686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:24:31.000Z","msg":"當然唔可以漏左杜小喬啦 雖然佢戲份唔多<br />\n我知道呢道應該有好多巴打唔鐘意佢<br />\n但都要Support下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bb529cc12b0db13e6e11046f2596ae5a80fa04","tid":143690,"uid":83257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:24:34.000Z","msg":"睇左 睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩同番子豪一齊"},{"pid":"eb61df0db121586a8fcbcdd3f4f555a44956b7aa","tid":143690,"uid":78686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左 睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩同番子豪一齊</blockquote><br />\n我以為佢最後都真係會揀韓國仔"}]}